&lt;h3&gt;About The Team&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Life360’s FP&amp;amp;A team is small, senior, and closely connected to how the company operates. We don’t sit on the sidelines. Finance is in the room when decisions get made, and the work we produce is what leadership relies on to run the business. We know a top-performing finance organization is a competitive advantage, and we&#39;re investing in the people, systems, and processes that get us there.&lt;/p&gt;
