&lt;h3&gt;About The Team&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Life360&#39;s Credit, Collections &amp;amp; Billing team is central to how the company gets paid. This isn&#39;t a back-office function that processes transactions in isolation. The decisions and effectiveness of this team drive cash flow, revenue quality, and how Life360 manages financial risk across the business.&lt;/p&gt;
